<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>cloudflared on 路飞博客</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/cloudflared/</link><description>Recent content in cloudflared on 路飞博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Sep 2023 13:13:16 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/cloudflared/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>cloudflared Tunnels 内网穿透</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/cloudflared-tunnels-%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Sep 2023 13:13:16 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/cloudflared-tunnels-%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;code>Cloudflared Tunnels&lt;/code>是Cloudflare提供的&lt;code>内网穿透&lt;/code>工具，可安全地将&lt;code>公网流量&lt;/code>转发到内部网络服务。通过加密隧道连接全球网络，它提供安全性和性能优化，方便访问内部服务。&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>部署环境: windows10&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h3 id="一-下载程序">一: 下载程序&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>将&lt;code>cloudflared-windows-amd64.exe&lt;/code> 重命名为将&lt;code>cloudflared.exe&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflared/releases/latest/download/cloudflared-windows-amd64.exe" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflared/releases/latest/download/cloudflared-windows-amd64.exe&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="二-拷贝项目">二: 拷贝项目&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>拷贝项目文件到本地任意目录:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>地址 : &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/woniu336/cloudflared" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://github.com/woniu336/cloudflared&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="三-启动服务">三: 启动服务&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>将&lt;code>cloudflared.exe&lt;/code>和项目文件放在同一个文件夹,&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然后双击 &lt;code>menu.bat&lt;/code> 开启你的穿透之旅吧&lt;/p>
&lt;br></description></item></channel></rss>